This \textit{pañjāpatra} from King Rājendra is an official, albeit reassuring-sounding summons to Cautarīyā Bhīma Vikrama Śāha and Cautarīyā Colonel Vīra Vikrama Śāha, who had fled from the kingdom after the Kot massacre.% image:#surface1
